        $quotes = array(
            "Take care of your body. It's the only place you have to live.", "To enjoy the glow of good health, you must exercise.", "Physical fitness is not only one of the most important keys to a healthy body, it is the basis of dynamic and creative intellectual activity.", "Reading is to the mind what exercise is to the body.", "The purpose of training is to tighten up the slack, toughen the body, and polish the spirit.", "Fitness is not about being better than someone else... It's about being better than you used to be.", "For me, fitness is not just about hitting the gym; it is also about an inner happiness and an overall well-being.", "I'm not in the best shape, but I want to prove to myself I can do something that seems insurmountable and inspire others by showing them no matter where they are in their fitness goals, they can do it, too.", "Time and health are two precious assets that we don't recognize and appreciate until they have been depleted.", "The human body is the best picture of the human soul.", "The reason I exercise is for the quality of life I enjoy.", "Walking is the best possible exercise. Habituate yourself to walk very far.", "In fitness, there are no short cuts. It involves immense discipline and hard work.", "The mind is the most important part of achieving any fitness goal. Mental change always comes before physical change.", "A lot of people are afraid of heights. Not me, I'm afraid of widths.", "A muscle is like a car. If you want it to run well early in the morning, you have to warm it up.", "Exercise to stimulate, not to annihilate. The world wasn't formed in a day, and neither were we. Set small goals and build upon them.", "True enjoyment comes from activity of the mind and exercise of the body; the two are ever united.", "Fitness starts at home. What you eat is what you will look, just as what you sow is what you reap. Eat good food: eat fruits, vegetables, healthy grains, and don't go for sweet and trite food.", "People talk about physical fitness, but mental health is equally important. I see people suffering, and their families feel a sense of shame about it, which doesn't help. One needs support and understanding. I am now working on an initiative to create awareness about anxiety and depression and help people.", "The typical response from people when I tell them I'm diabetic is, 'Oh, I'm sorry to hear that.' You know, I'm not. I'm a better athlete because of diabetes rather than despite it. I'm more aware of my training, my fitness and more aware of nutrition. I'm more proactive about my health.", "Health is the thing that makes you feel that now is the best time of the year.", "I've always believed fitness is an entry point to help you build that happier, healthier life. When your health is strong, you're capable of taking risks. You'll feel more confident to ask for the promotion. You'll have more energy to be a better mom. You'll feel more deserving of love.", "Bodybuilding is much like any other sport. To be successful, you must dedicate yourself 100% to your training, diet and mental approach.", "You can always improve your fitness if you keep training.", "Swimming is normal for me. I'm relaxed. I'm comfortable, and I know my surroundings. It's my home.", "Exercise should be regarded as tribute to the heart.", "Leave all the afternoon for exercise and recreation, which are as necessary as reading. I will rather say more necessary because health is worth more than learning.", "Fitness is not an option. It's part of my job.", "The value and utility of any experiment are determined by the fitness of the material to the purpose for which it is used, and thus in the case before us it cannot be immaterial what plants are subjected to experiment and in what manner such experiment is conducted.", "If I don't feel confident about my body, I'm not going to sit at home and feel sorry for myself and not do something about it. It's all about taking action and not being lazy. So you do the work